[[File:Seal of Haagenti.jpg|thumb|Seal of Haagenti from ''[[The Lesser Key of Solomon]]'']]

In [[demonology]], '''Haagenti''' is a Great President of [[Hell]], ruling thirty-three legions of [[demon]]s. He makes men wise by instructing them in every subject, transmutes all metals into [[gold]], and changes wine into water and water into wine.

Haagenti is depicted as a big bull with the wings of a [[griffin]], changing into a man under request of the [[Evocation|conjurer]].

Also called "Haage"/"Hgog".{{cn|date=October 2011}}

